    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h2 id="references">Documentation References</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Specification</strong>: <code>.zencoder/chats/f1ab716d-44a5-40f6-b243-196179e16ee3/spec.md</code></li>
                <li><strong>Architecture Decisions</strong>: <code>.zencoder/chats/f1ab716d-44a5-40f6-b243-196179e16ee3/ARCHITECTURE_DECISIONS.md</code></li>
