    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h2 id="notes">Notes</h2>
            <p>This project emphasizes <strong>code reuse</strong> and <strong>minimal schema changes</strong>. Backward compatibility is critical — existing functionality must not break. Admin-only access simplifies permission model. Task dependencies benefit entire Todo system, not just DailyPlan.</p>
        </div>
